<Layout title="About Me" description="Learn more about my professional background, skills, and experience">
  <div class="about-page">
    <section class="about-hero">
      <div class="about-hero-content">
        <h1>About Me</h1>
        <p class="lead">Software engineer and product manager with a passion for building innovative solutions.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-content">
          <h2>My Story</h2>
          <p>I'm a passionate software engineer and product manager with over 10 years of experience in the tech industry. I specialize in building scalable web applications and leading product development teams.</p>
          
          <p>Throughout my career, I've worked with startups and established companies to deliver user-centered products that solve real problems. I believe in the power of technology to transform businesses and improve people's lives.</p>
          
          <p>My approach combines technical expertise with strategic thinking and user empathy. I thrive in collaborative environments where I can leverage my skills to build products that users love.</p>
          
          <h3>Professional Philosophy</h3>
          <p>I believe that great products come from a deep understanding of user needs, technical excellence, and thoughtful design. My goal is always to create solutions that are not only functional but also delightful to use.</p>
        </div>
        
